OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunshine and
OL,6,Fblustery showers continuing this
OL,7,Fevening, some of the showers may be
OL,8,Fheavy and thundery at times. Drier
OL,9,Fconditions for a time but showers may
OL,10,Freturn by the morning. A chilly night
OL,11,Fespecially in rural parts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with perhaps
OL,14,Fone or two showers in the morning.
OL,15,FShowers becoming more widespread and
OL,16,Fpotentially turning heavy and thundery
OL,17,Fin places by the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
